  'Uncover vs Oliva Skin Clinic — a side-by-side breakdown',
  'uncover-vs-oliva-skin-clinic',
  'Honest comparison of Uncover and Oliva — qualifications, services, pricing approach, and presence in Delhi NCR. Written for patients choosing between them.',
  '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Oliva is one of the larger skincare chains in India, particularly strong in South India. Patients in Delhi NCR often ask how Uncover compares. Here''s a factual breakdown based on public information.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textFormat": 0, "textStyle": ""}, {"type": "heading", "tag": "h2", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Qualification model", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Uncover is dermatologist-led — MD DVL or DNB at every consultation, dermatologist supervision on every procedure. Oliva advertises a team of dermatologists; delivery across its network varies by location. If dermatologist-led delivery across the full procedure matters to you, confirm at the specific clinic.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textFormat": 0, "textStyle": ""}, {"type": "heading", "tag": "h2", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Service overlap", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "list", "tag": "ul", "start": 1, "listType": "bullet", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "direction": "ltr", "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Laser hair removal", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "HydraFacial", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 3, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Acne and pigmentation", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 4, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Hair loss treatment (PRP, GFC)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 5, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Anti-aging treatments", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}]}, {"type": "heading", "tag": "h2", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Where Uncover is distinct", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "list", "tag": "ul", "start": 1, "listType": "bullet", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "direction": "ltr", "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "AI skin analysis at every consultation", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "FUE hair transplant", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 3, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Body contouring (HIFU, EMS+RF)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 4, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Transparent published starting prices", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}]}, {"type": "heading", "tag": "h2", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pricing approach", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Both clinics offer packaged pricing. Uncover publishes starting prices for each treatment online. Oliva pricing varies by clinic and is typically shared at consultation. Request itemised quotes at both.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textFormat": 0, "textStyle": ""}, {"type": "heading", "tag": "h2", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Delhi NCR footprint", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Oliva has a smaller Delhi NCR footprint than in South India; check their website for current Delhi NCR locations. Uncover runs 8 clinics across Delhi, Gurgaon, and Noida. Proximity often decides the right pick.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textFormat": 0, "textStyle": ""}, {"type": "heading", "tag": "h2", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "How to choose", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr"}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If AI skin analysis and dermatologist-led delivery across every step matters, or you''re specifically looking for FUE transplant or body contouring, Uncover fits. If you''re established with Oliva and happy, no reason to switch for the sake of it. Compare free consultation plans from both and pick what fits your specific treatment need.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textFormat": 0, "textStyle": ""}], "direction": "ltr"}}'::jsonb,
